          ],
          "parameters": {
            "color": 7,
            "width": 672,
            "height": 240,
            "content": "📝 PHASE 2: Transcript Download & Transformation\n\nThis phase processes the extracted transcription:\n\n1. Download XML file from obtained URL\n2. Convert XML to JSON\n3. Decode HTML entities\n4. Concatenate full text\n5. Count words\n\n✅ Output: Clean fullTranscript ready to use"
          },
          "typeVersion": 1
        }
